{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_08_01_short",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 ミクは凄いね (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　嘘でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? No way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……いきなりどうしたんだ？）\n（あっちに誰かいるのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…What’s gotten into her all of a sudden?）\n（Is there someone over there?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8220801728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あの人は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That person is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.226856478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "初音ミク……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hatsune Miku…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9682850996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが、ライブツアーのために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――When LizNoir came to Hokkaido",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8269928533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "北海道にやってきた時のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for their live tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6669926132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0869919378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、さっきは驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I was surprised earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9936600922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "東京からはるばる北海道まで来たからには\nそりゃ、何か面白いことがないかなって期待してたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we came all the way from Tokyo to Hokkaido‚\nI was hoping for something interesting to happen‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8904928006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0405990044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、街でばったりミクに会うとは思わなかったよ\n期待してた以上の驚きだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I never expected to run into Miku on the street.\nIt was a bigger surprise than I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3554287354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、葵もミクを知ってたんだな\nミクの動画を観てた感じもなかったし、意外だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ you knew Miku‚ huh‚ Aoi?\nI didn’t think you watched her videos‚ so it was a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕の方こそ、君があんなに驚くとは思わなかったよ\nまぁ、事務所で聴いてたことはないから仕方ないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised that you were so surprised.\nWell‚ I guess it’s understandable since you’ve never heard of her at the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.500711894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "大体ゲーセンで音ゲーをやって覚えたからね\nミクの曲は大人気で、沢山収録されてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mostly learned about her from playing rhythm games at the arcade.\nHer songs are very popular‚ so they’re included in a lot of games.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}